{"tid":2071912,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"校園神正妹！越南網紅穿「學校制服」太性感引發議論，換上私服曬超長「事業線」","createTime":"2020-06-20T08:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T08:45:43.000Z","uid":217211,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a88c7def36546064e66f1427dd9c953b28041ae3","tid":2071912,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGuiVbM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGuiVbM.png&h=1907058e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青春時期大家成長速度不同，同學們之間最常比較身高和體重，其中女孩們的「發育」變化也令人難為情，來自越南的 Phan Thị Bảo Tr&acirc;n 就是最真實的例子，據外媒報導，這位越南正妹還是一名學生，卻因為平時穿奧黛上課的樣子被拍下留影，在網上造成轟動！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/egw5AbD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fegw5AbD.jpg&h=89950f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你沒看錯！有著超級純潔的天使面孔，和魔鬼般傲人身材的她，還是一名學生啊！在學期間就曾因為豐滿身材備受矚目而感到不適應，因為學校規定上學要穿著奧黛制服，反而更顯凹凸有致的身材，一開始會聽到同學之間的議論，後來甚至在網上都會收到被冒犯或不好聽的言論，這讓年紀輕輕的她一度不敢與人交談。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJSZDC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJSZDC.png&h=4190ea4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8E9ZEDD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8E9ZEDD.jpg&h=2838172f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她表示經過長久以來的自我調適，習慣大家對她的異樣眼光，將重心轉向學習、聽音樂和看電影等其他興趣，如今不僅接受眾人的目光大方秀身材，還轉為一位學生網紅，一張張火辣照片吸引破八萬人追蹤，建立起自信後，Phan Thị Bảo Tr&acirc;n 甚至還收到模特兒邀約，成為一名校園紅人！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVKSfb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVKSfb3.jpg&h=ed00a88f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQZnCqo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQZnCqo.png&h=6a792930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A269hqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA269hqp.jpg&h=cfa61ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MV9fcYL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMV9fcYL.jpg&h=a16014cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzkVcYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzkVcYM.jpg&h=0d2134d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且，近日她還在自介放上「I don&rsquo;t have a boyfriend」，說明目前單身中，好像意味著大家可以勇於追求，讓廣大網友紛紛自告奮勇，在文章下方留言自薦，有興趣的人不妨可以到她的 IG 追蹤一下呦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqHo6iS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqHo6iS.jpg&h=369f1293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSY7Oxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSY7Oxc.jpg&h=4fcc8f42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rieyJ5y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrieyJ5y.jpg&h=bc66fca7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87913c7eccff2bedd0b31d31697ff7c3362f6820","tid":2071912,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"求ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0b8923aa089de06b55ff2225fdccdcea26b32f","tid":2071912,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87913c7eccff2bedd0b31d31697ff7c3362f6820","tid":2071912,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"求ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"baotran.16tui  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00b5f7e57b361691a18e688ea3a22250d240d88","tid":2071912,"uid":3405,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"有幾張好似馬蹄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad621960816cd71df25b7163e